Distribution. Collected at Ashmore Reef and Herald Cays on the Great Barrier Reef of Australia , Fiji , Palau , and Enewetok Atoll in the Marshall Islands (
Fig. 48
). A fairly rarely collected species from depths of 10–53 m , probably more widely distributed in the western Pacific than current records suggest.

Three specimens from Palau differed by a minimum of 9 % of the CO 1 genome from the three other species mentioned above (
Winterbottom et al. , 2014
).
